pcd8544
symptom: nothing on the screen
possible cause: wrong connection
solution: check order of cables
possible cause: data not passed properly
solution: check electrical connections
possible cause: wrong initialization
solution: check if there's voltage on VOut capacitor. if there is, switch to basic instruction set mode and send normal screen
    if there's no voltage, set voltage or try other options
possible cause: lousy internal connection
solution: check if there's voltage on VOut. press the top metal. squeeze the top metal.

symptom: horizontal line on disconnection
possible cause:???
solution: squeeze the top bar

symptom: screen goes gradually black
possible cause: VOut goes uncontrollably high
solution: insert a capacitor between VOut and GND
